This is stupid its not even close to the correct way to clean your hands.

1. Lather hands with lots of soap.
2. Scratch fingers inside palm of hand to clean your finger nails.
3.Scrub every finger individually going around them using your other hand . Do so with both hands.
4. Rub the sides of your hands and fingers as if you were tracing them.
5. Rince your hands thoroughly without touching them together.
6. Close water without touching it with your hands because the bacteries that you might have put there when you opened it will get back on your hands most likely.
